name: E-cell Website of NITJ
description: Built this static website for the entrepreneur's society (E-cell) of my institute. The website is used to list our upcoming events and details about the society.

name: Amazon Clone
description: Replicated some features of Amazon like signing up, browsing products, adding them to cart and checking out the subtotal.

name: Instagram Clone
description: Replicated some major features of Instagram like uploading pictures and commenting on them.

name: Mechanical Department Website of NITJ
description: Contributed in building this website of my department along with some seniors. This website is again rebuild my be with new UI and integrated admin panel, but it is yet to be deployed.

name: U-store (OLD)
description: This is the very first prototype of my startup idea (U-store) built using old tech stack. The idea is to provide a platform on which students can buy/sell within their college domain in a very simple way.

name: ToDo App
description: Features: (1) Sign in with Google (2) Add a ToDo (3) Edit a ToDo (4) Mark ToDo as Done or in Progress (5) Delete a ToDo (6) Logout

name: COVID-19 Tracker
description: This web-app consumes an API which provides latest COVID-19 stats which is used to plot graphs that can be filtered based on any specific country. API used: https://covid19.mathdro.id/api

name: WhatsApp Clone
description: An exact Whatsapp clone in terms of UI along with group chat and login with Google feature. The groups will be password protected so that only authorized members can join a group and start interaction.

name: Twitter Lite
description: Replicated some major features of Twitter like tweeting, commenting and liking tweets using MERN stack with GraphQL and authentication using JSON web-tokens (JWT).

name: Linkmee
description: This web-app solves the problem of sharing small files and links between computers and smartphones. The app has Google login so that each user has their own private space to store links/files and access them anywhere when needed, in just one-click.

name: Blue Chat
description: A simple chat app based on rooms where a user can create new rooms or join any existing one to start chatting with other members in the room.

name: WanderLust
description: Full-stack travelling website with integrated admin panel from where all the content of the website can be modified and can manage bookings. Admin credentials: username - admin | password - admin

name: YupKart
description: Full-stack e-commerce website with integrated payment gateway(PayPal) and admin panel to upload/remove products and manage user orders. Admin credentials: username - admin | password - admin

name: DevStation
description: Full-stack social media platform for developers to connect and build productive communities. It has user's profile section to add skills, experiences and social links. The profile section also lists top 5 repos of the user from his/her Github.

name: U-store
description: This full-stack website is the actual implementation of my startup idea which is a platform to buy and sell within college domain. This is the second(final) prototype of my idea.

name: Rendezvous - Video Calling App
description: The app allows connecting one-to-one video calling by just using a unique identification code that can be copied from the copy button and just send to the other person to start a video call.
